title: Legal Reserve Ratio for Germany
notes:
Series Is Presented Here As Four Variables--(1)--Original Data, 1876-1914 (2)--Seasonally Adjusted Data, 1876-1914 (3)--Original Data, 1924-1935 (4)--Seasonally Adjusted, 1924-1935. Data Were Computed From Metallic Reserve Added To Treasury Notes Divided By Reichsbak Note Circulation. Source: Computed By NBER From Data In Centralblatt; Verwaltungs Bericht Der Reichsbank; Wirtschaft Und Statistik; Die Reichsbank.

This NBER data series m14093 appears on the NBER website in Chapter 14 at http://www.nber.org/databases/macrohistory/contents/chapter14.html.
